---
title: Pineappley Pork Meatloaves with a Sweet Potato & Bell Pepper Jumble
description: Sweet and savory is a combo we can always get behind (for dinner, dessert, and snacks—hello, Chicago-style popcorn). This week, our ode to the dynamic flavor duo takes the form of personal-portioned pork meatloaves glazed with a mix of hoisin and pineapple juice. On the side, there’s roasted sweet potatoes, bell pepper, and caramelized pineapple chunks. After one bite, your taste buds will be lighting up like a pinball machine.
